title: I LOVE JHIN

embed.description: I am in love. Jhin the new League of Legends champion, I have no words that can explain, but I do have Kpop! enjoy the show. Poop Social Media FB https://www.facebook.com/Markaayy IG @Markaayy Outro JPB x Mendum - Feelings

body: So recently I tried out Jhin (The new champion) and fell in love instantly. Although his ULT still trips me out, he is a lot of fun. I hope you guys can check out my latest video and leave a comment. Love to hear your feedback on Jhin. Poop.
